| work = Ynet
| accessdate = 2008-03-14
| date = 2005-05-11
| url = http://www.ynet.co.il/articles/0,7340,L-3083171,00.html
}} {{he icon}}</ref> and was chosen the most influential woman in Israeli culture in the 2008 "Woman" festival in [[Holon]].<ref name=shaviv>{{Cite news
| last = Shaviv
| first = Miriam
